metadata.name: GARDEN OF THE HESPERIDES
metadata.description: Deep in the thickets of a beautiful fertile island is a garden in which the golden apples of eternal youth grow. Laughter and music are always heard from the garden, to which the nymphs Hesperides dances, being under the gaze of a hundred-headed dragon. An ideal world that is separated by waters and protected by a huge monster seems out of reach for uninvited guests and prying eyes. Nothing will dare disturb this blissful stillness until...
